 @{b}History@{ub}

@{u}NewEdit 1.16@{uu}
 - NEW: Filename-Completion
 - NEW: Control-a to jump to the beginning of a line
 - three small bugfixes in the installer script
 - bugfixes for some functions which didn't eat their own command key codes

@{u}NewEdit 1.15@{uu}
 - NEW: Options NOCONTROL, NOESC, CALCKEY, CASEKEY, COUNTKEY,
                DATEKEY and TIMEKEY
 - NEW: Control-d and Control-e commands
 - NEW: Support for different keymaps
 - NEW: German AmigaGuide
 - NEW: Installer script
 - source improved

@{u}NewEdit 1.11 (not released - Paul was faster ;-)@{uu}
 - NEW: Included improvements of Paul Huxham.
 - NEW: Evaluation of mathematical expressions via "calculus.library"
